<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>1986-02-28</DATELINE><TITLE>CNS Tuberculosis</TITLE><BODY>Tuberculous meningitis is a subacute meningitis in which early therapy significantly improves outcome. Atypical features abound, and the diagnosis must be entertained in a variety of situations. CT scanning has improved our knowledge of the disease and may help in diagnosis.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>